### 第一次上报：RUNNING
POST http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskId": "TASK-001",
  "shopId": "SHOP-001",
  "platform": "TAOBAO",
  "status": "RUNNING",
  "startedAt": "2026-07-10T09:00:00",
  "finishedAt": null,
  "rowCount": 0,
  "errorMessage": null
}

### 相同 taskId 更新为 SUCCESS
POST http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskId": "TASK-001",
  "shopId": "SHOP-001",
  "platform": "TAOBAO",
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "startedAt": "2026-07-10T09:00:00",
  "finishedAt": "2026-07-10T09:10:00",
  "rowCount": 1200,
  "errorMessage": null
}

### 默认分页查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs?page=1&size=10

### shopId 筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs?page=1&size=10&shopId=SHOP-001

### status 筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs?page=1&size=10&status=SUCCESS

### 组合筛选
GET http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs?page=1&size=10&shopId=SHOP-001&status=SUCCESS

### 店铺汇总
GET http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs/summary?shopId=SHOP-001

### 非法 status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs?page=1&size=10&status=UNKNOWN

### 非法 taskId
POST http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskId": " ",
  "shopId": "SHOP-001",
  "platform": "TAOBAO",
  "status": "RUNNING",
  "startedAt": "2026-07-10T09:00:00",
  "finishedAt": null,
  "rowCount": 0,
  "errorMessage": null
}

### 非法 rowCount
POST http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskId": "TASK-BAD-ROW",
  "shopId": "SHOP-001",
  "platform": "TAOBAO",
  "status": "RUNNING",
  "startedAt": "2026-07-10T09:00:00",
  "finishedAt": null,
  "rowCount": -1,
  "errorMessage": null
}

### SUCCESS 缺少 finishedAt
POST http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskId": "TASK-BAD-SUCCESS",
  "shopId": "SHOP-001",
  "platform": "TAOBAO",
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "startedAt": "2026-07-10T09:00:00",
  "finishedAt": null,
  "rowCount": 100,
  "errorMessage": null
}

### FAILED 缺少 errorMessage
POST http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskId": "TASK-BAD-FAILED",
  "shopId": "SHOP-001",
  "platform": "DOUYIN",
  "status": "FAILED",
  "startedAt": "2026-07-10T09:00:00",
  "finishedAt": "2026-07-10T09:10:00",
  "rowCount": 0,
  "errorMessage": null
}

### 非法 page
GET http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs?page=0&size=10

### 非法 size
GET http://localhost:8080/api/task-runs?page=1&size=101
